{"tid":536741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第五被告黃家駒承認一項暴動罪","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T06:17:29.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86f96207dc9f9517219c3e2b9e214ed14249539a","tid":536741,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"香港電台-港聞\t<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t2018年1月22日 下午12:47<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前年年初發生的旺角騷亂，包括本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦等六名被告被控暴動、襲警等罪，案件在高等法院再提訊。<br />\n<br />\n法庭聽取各被告答辯，首被告梁天琦承認一項襲警罪，但否認其餘的兩項暴動罪和一項煽惑暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n第五被告黃家駒承認一項暴動罪，但否認一項襲警罪，獲控方接受。其餘四名被告，分別面對暴動及非法集結罪，他們全部否認控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AD%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%BC%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E8%A8%8A-044733786.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%2596%25BC%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E8%25A8%258A-044733786.html&d=2sqDBBqJzP5ZBWXjfw5LSf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=86738fe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AD%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%BC%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E8%A8%8A-044733786.html</a>"},{"pid":"e5ca21a8b56622d0ba35484bc924d682184e47e2","tid":536741,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"今天我✌️"},{"pid":"510e3f24d7175432ecc1d79bdec1390f7d8c8e74","tid":536741,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit